- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses optimal control and neural networks to learn the policy. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with underactuated systems and optimizing local controllers. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with learning a policy for a dynamic task. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve vision-based sensing for the locomotion task.
